		5.1 ==> if flag 'R' exits [add dir to head of list attent dir]

flags want be creating [l R a r t] and [G U S --no_sort]
		l==> long list
		R==> recursively list
		a==> include hiddens files
		r==> revers list
		t==> sort by modified time

		G==> use colors
		U==> sort by creation time
		S==> sort by files size
		no_sort ==> stop sort
